name: Emptying/Emerging
question: What aspect of your Object-Self is in an Emptying/Emerging state. How are you navigating this state? Did you consciously initiate it? Or did some external factor signals into this state?

name: Doing/Producing
question: What is actively taking shape in Manifestation? What aspect of your Object Self is involved here?

name: Embodying/Attuning
question: What aspect of your Object-Self is embodying and attuning? What is supporting it and what is posing as challenge?

name: Shedding/Composting
question: What aspect of your Object-Self is shedding and composting? What factor initiates this phase? Is it internal or external?
